title: New NFL fad, Super Bowl prediction, and Russell Westbrook
itunes:title: New NFL fad, Super Bowl prediction, and Russell Westbrook
description:
Colin discusses why he doesn't like the new young head coach fad in the NFL, his thoughts on the new head coaching hires, his Super Bowl prediction, and more proof the Oklahoma City Thunder can't control PG Russell Westbrook. Guests include Nick Wright, Peter King, Robb Parker, and Casey Hayward.
